# validate-prd-traceability wiring rule

Run `signalos validate-prd-traceability --json` before treating PRD coverage as
complete.

- Every row must resolve to BELIEF, BUILD, DEC, or DEFER.
- BELIEF and BUILD rows must point to live Belief IDs.
- DEC rows must point to live DECISION-DNA blocks.
- DEFER rows must use `DEFER -> WNN` or `DEFER -> never`.
- Principle-shaped PRD claims need measurable Belief signal thresholds or must
  be reclassified as decisions.
